## Routing

See `.claude/CLAUDE.md` for the full routing table — which folder and workflow to consult
for any given task.

**Quick reference:**

| I want to… | Go to… |
|------------|--------|
| Write or review code | `code/docs/CODING-PRINCIPLES.md` |
| Add a new module | `code/workflows/01-new-module/` |
| Write tests first | `code/workflows/02-tdd-cycle/` |
| Cut a release | `code/workflows/06-release-process/` |
| Set up the project | `how-to/workflows/01-setup/` |
| Review a PR | `project-management/workflows/05-code-review/` |
| Run a security audit | `project-management/workflows/06-security-audit/` |

## Gap register

`GAPS.md` lists every workflow folder that has a `CONTEXT.md` but is missing `STEPS.md`
or `CHECKLIST.md`. Fill gaps with: `/scaffold --fill-gaps <workflow-path>`
